All right, okay.

28:38.150 --> 28:40.119
XIOMARA:
He's eating again?

28:40.152 --> 28:42.421
Yeah, he must not
have gotten enough.

28:42.454 --> 28:44.156
Why don't we just
give him one bottle?

28:44.190 --> 28:46.258
No, I don't want to.

28:46.292 --> 28:48.094
But, baby, you're exhausted.

28:48.127 --> 28:49.495
You haven't slept
in 48 hours.

28:49.528 --> 28:51.130
I'm his mom.

28:51.163 --> 28:53.099
I have to stay strong.

28:53.132 --> 28:56.836
Mothers don't always
have to be strong.

28:59.305 --> 29:01.307
Hon.

29:03.309 --> 29:05.344
I'm sorry.

29:05.377 --> 29:07.947
Just think I'm a
little overwhelmed.

29:07.980 --> 29:10.049
And I'd be okay,
if I knew it was working,

29:10.082 --> 29:13.385
but he just keeps crying,
like he's hungry.

29:13.419 --> 29:15.788
Look, I get all the great
reasons to nurse,

29:15.822 --> 29:17.089
but if it isn't working...

29:17.123 --> 29:19.191
But I have to
make it work.

29:19.225 --> 29:21.060
It can't be my trauma
getting in the way.

29:21.093 --> 29:24.363
Why?
Because what happened
is my fault.

29:24.396 --> 29:28.267
I mean, my maternal instincts,
where were they?

29:28.300 --> 29:30.136
I just gave him
to the nurse.

29:30.169 --> 29:31.403
Baby...

29:31.437 --> 29:33.806
she was wearing a uniform.

29:33.840 --> 29:35.407
She said he needed
a hearing test.

29:35.441 --> 29:37.944
But I should've known.

29:37.977 --> 29:40.913
And I didn't.

29:40.947 --> 29:43.916
And I know
it doesn't make sense,

29:43.950 --> 29:46.953
but I just want to be able
to do this for him.

29:46.986 --> 29:50.422
I just want to be able
to do this one good thing.

29:50.456 --> 29:52.825
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
 And even though Xo agreed,

29:52.859 --> 29:54.894
it really didn't
 make any sense,

29:54.927 --> 29:57.596
she too wanted to do something
 good for her child.

29:57.629 --> 29:59.465
How can I help?

30:01.533 --> 30:03.335
When he opens his mouth,

30:03.369 --> 30:06.405
will you stuff my boob in it
like it's a hamburger?

30:06.438 --> 30:08.574
Honey, I am all over it.

30:08.607 --> 30:11.844
And it should be noted,
 she was.

30:11.878 --> 30:13.412
(baby crying)
 And then she was again.

30:13.445 --> 30:16.115
And... stuff.

30:16.148 --> 30:17.316
And yet... again.

30:17.349 --> 30:19.418
And stuff.

30:19.451 --> 30:21.487
RAFAEL:
 Is everything okay?

30:21.520 --> 30:23.089
We don't know.

30:23.122 --> 30:24.423
He's nursing
every 30 minutes.

30:24.456 --> 30:26.025
I must be doing
something wrong.

30:26.058 --> 30:27.426
Maybe he's cluster feeding.

30:27.459 --> 30:30.362
Which brings us back, here.

30:32.164 --> 30:34.433
Come on,
 did you doubt Michael?

30:34.466 --> 30:35.968
He's a mensch.

30:36.002 --> 30:38.104
Get a book and read it

30:38.137 --> 30:39.538
so you know
what you're talking about.

30:39.571 --> 30:41.440
Then wait for the right moment,

30:41.473 --> 30:43.976
when she doesn't know
and her mom doesn't know,

30:44.010 --> 30:45.511
and even Abuela is stumped,

30:45.544 --> 30:48.514
that's when you come in
with the save.

30:48.547 --> 30:50.482
Cluster feeding.
Uh, it's like when a baby eats

30:50.516 --> 30:52.618
and eats before the mature milk
comes in.

30:52.651 --> 30:55.254
I read it here.

31:04.396 --> 31:07.533
My milk is coming in.

31:07.566 --> 31:10.402
Oh, my God,
my milk is coming in!

31:10.436 --> 31:12.571
(laughing)
Your milk is coming in!

31:17.576 --> 31:18.577
Nice work.

31:18.610 --> 31:21.380
Yes. Family fist bump.

31:21.413 --> 31:22.514
Family fist bump.

31:28.254 --> 31:29.555
Look who's cluster feeding?

31:29.588 --> 31:32.258
Yeah? And pooping.

31:32.291 --> 31:35.194
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
 Papa time.

31:35.227 --> 31:36.929
I insist on changing
his diaper.

31:36.963 --> 31:39.265
I just need someone to tell me
exactly how to do it.

31:39.298 --> 31:40.566
I'll help.

31:40.599 --> 31:43.335
Thanks, Dad.

31:43.369 --> 31:45.404
Oh...

31:47.273 --> 31:49.341
His first smile.

31:49.375 --> 31:52.178
Oh, how sweet...

31:52.211 --> 31:54.280
the way that none of them
 told him it was just gas.

31:54.313 --> 31:56.415
Okay, so I should take off.

31:56.448 --> 31:57.583
Uh, wait.

31:57.616 --> 31:59.285
I just wanted to thank you.

31:59.318 --> 32:01.320
You know,
for your advice earlier.

32:01.353 --> 32:03.355
Aw, he's a mensch, too.

32:03.389 --> 32:04.991
No problem.

32:05.024 --> 32:07.226
What advise?

32:07.259 --> 32:08.660
I was just having
a little trouble

32:08.694 --> 32:11.263
figuring out my place,
you know, with your family.

32:11.297 --> 32:13.132
Oh?

32:13.165 --> 32:14.700
It's just, you guys
are all so close, you know?

32:14.733 --> 32:16.402
No, I get that.

32:16.435 --> 32:18.037
RAFAEL: And I know we
are trying to get back

32:18.070 --> 32:20.406
to normal, but it's
not normal what happened.

32:20.439 --> 32:22.241
Yeah, you're right.
And plus, we didn't even

32:22.274 --> 32:23.976
discuss what our normal would be
and even if we did,

32:24.010 --> 32:25.577
I don't know if it
would count, because

32:25.611 --> 32:28.447
how do you know how you feel
unless you're here?

32:28.480 --> 32:30.416
How do you feel?

32:30.449 --> 32:32.384
Like I don't want
to be away from Mateo.

32:32.418 --> 32:34.987
So, do you want to stay over?

32:35.021 --> 32:37.356
Like, for... like the
first couple weeks?

32:37.389 --> 32:39.291
Wow.

32:39.325 --> 32:41.693
I was angling for, like,
a 6:00 a.m. in, 11:00 p.m. out.

32:41.727 --> 32:43.562
What?
Yes.

32:43.595 --> 32:45.397
Great.
Great.

32:45.431 --> 32:47.466
Dude, options two and three

32:47.499 --> 32:49.168
were just sitting there.

32:49.201 --> 32:50.602
(phone swooshes)

32:50.636 --> 32:54.306
Oh, I, uh, still have
Rogelio's phone.

32:56.408 --> 32:57.576
What?

32:59.578 --> 33:01.413
Someone tweeted a photo.

33:01.447 --> 33:03.482
Oh, God, of Mateo?

33:03.515 --> 33:05.284
WOMAN:
 Move into the sun a little bit.

33:05.317 --> 33:08.187
Indirect sunlight is good
for them in the first days.

33:08.220 --> 33:10.389
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
 Let it be known that any doubts
 about her maternal instincts

33:10.422 --> 33:12.558
shattered at this moment,
 and Jane had one thought

33:12.591 --> 33:14.560
and one thought only.

33:14.593 --> 33:16.395
Hey, whoa, whoa, whoa,
Jane, where are you going?

33:16.428 --> 33:17.363
To shut this down.

33:17.396 --> 33:18.364
Wait, how?

33:18.397 --> 33:20.732
I have no idea.

33:20.766 --> 33:22.434
(crowd clamoring)

33:22.468 --> 33:24.370
And that's when it hit her--

33:24.403 --> 33:26.405
a beam of divine inspiration.

33:26.438 --> 33:28.640
Okay, honestly, the beam
 was just a reflection

33:28.674 --> 33:31.477
coming off
 Slutty Crystal's compact,

33:31.510 --> 33:34.246
but was that just luck
 or divine providence?

33:34.280 --> 33:36.248
Well, that's for theologians
 to debate.

33:36.282 --> 33:38.717
But the fact remained that
 if her makeup wasn't smudged

33:38.750 --> 33:40.519
from sweaty car sex,

33:40.552 --> 33:42.521
Crystal wouldn't
 have had to fix it.

33:42.554 --> 33:44.690
And the light
 wouldn't have shown,

33:44.723 --> 33:47.293
providing the answer
 to Jane's problem.

33:51.497 --> 33:52.331
Jane, hello.

33:52.364 --> 33:53.432
Sister Margaret?

33:53.465 --> 33:55.201
Here's the thing.

33:55.234 --> 33:57.303
I didn't want
to come out here before,

33:57.336 --> 33:59.771
'cause the truth is

33:59.805 --> 34:02.074
I've had sex.

34:02.108 --> 34:03.475
A lot.

34:03.509 --> 34:05.211
In cars even.

34:05.244 --> 34:07.279
I just didn't want my grandma
to know, but with all this,

34:07.313 --> 34:08.647
I decided to tell her the truth.

34:08.679 --> 34:10.581
So, now I'm telling you.

34:10.616 --> 34:12.484
I don't believe you.

34:12.518 --> 34:13.819
Well, it's true.

34:13.851 --> 34:15.121
And regardless,

34:15.154 --> 34:16.487
do you want to be involved

34:16.522 --> 34:17.523
in a public debate
about my virginity?

34:17.556 --> 34:21.360
I mean, doesn't
that sound archaic?

34:21.393 --> 34:23.094
What?

34:27.666 --> 34:29.501
Oh, my God!

34:29.534 --> 34:31.437
I'm leaking milk!

34:31.469 --> 34:34.473
Actually leaking!

34:34.505 --> 34:37.243
You want to see a miracle?

34:37.275 --> 34:40.246
This is a friggin' miracle!

34:42.281 --> 34:44.216
(whoops)
Look at this!

34:44.250 --> 34:45.516
Look at this!

34:45.551 --> 34:46.552
PETRA:
 It's really over.

34:46.585 --> 34:49.155
And I don't want it to be.

34:49.188 --> 34:51.857
And I, I just, I feel like...

34:51.889 --> 34:53.525
I don't know,
I think, I think

34:53.559 --> 34:55.161
maybe I just feel
a little lonely.

34:55.194 --> 34:56.527
You know?

34:56.562 --> 34:58.397
I am so sorry, sweetheart,

34:58.430 --> 35:00.599
that things are
so difficult for you.

35:10.776 --> 35:12.744
Mm, that's life.

35:12.778 --> 35:16.148
At times, you have to let go
of the peoples you love.

35:16.182 --> 35:18.184
Now, do the reasonable thing.

35:18.217 --> 35:20.819
Sell Rafael's sperm back to him.

35:20.852 --> 35:22.488
I'm not selling it, Mother.

35:22.521 --> 35:23.722
Your choice.

35:23.755 --> 35:25.557
Just move on.

35:25.591 --> 35:27.293
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
 Which for the record,

35:27.326 --> 35:29.661
she was trying to do when...

35:29.695 --> 35:31.497
Hey, I want to schedule

35:31.530 --> 35:33.332
a makeup meeting
with the bankers.

35:33.365 --> 35:34.666
My brother's mad at me
and I just...

35:34.700 --> 35:36.935
You okay?

35:36.968 --> 35:39.805
Please, stop pretending
to my friend, Luisa.

35:39.838 --> 35:41.607
I heard you

35:41.640 --> 35:43.642
the other night
talking to Rafael, okay?

35:43.675 --> 35:45.444
I mean, I feel a little bad

35:45.477 --> 35:46.645
about manipulating Petra,

35:46.678 --> 35:48.780
but I have a family now

35:48.814 --> 35:50.682
with Jane.

35:50.716 --> 35:52.684
And you walked away?

35:52.718 --> 35:54.453
Yes, of course, I walked away.

35:54.486 --> 35:56.322
And was it divine providence
 that these two

35:56.355 --> 35:57.923
met at this moment...

35:57.956 --> 35:59.658
Then you missed Raf saying
how he had no choice.

35:59.691 --> 36:01.660
Jane insisted.

36:01.693 --> 36:03.695
...when Luisa was determined
 to find some way

36:03.729 --> 36:06.365
to help her brother
 with his Petra situation.

36:06.398 --> 36:07.899
And then, I asked him,
point blank--

36:07.933 --> 36:09.768
if all things were even
who he wished he was with.

36:09.801 --> 36:13.239
What did he say?

36:13.272 --> 36:14.906
Well again, that's for
 theologians to debate.

36:14.940 --> 36:16.608
But the fact remains--

36:16.642 --> 36:18.744
the following events
 did exactly transpire.

36:18.777 --> 36:20.779
He got mad at me, actually.

36:20.812 --> 36:23.749
Because if I hadn't screwed up
in the first place,

36:23.782 --> 36:26.685
then none of this would be
happening, which... it's true.

36:26.718 --> 36:30.356
I mean,
that should have been your baby.

36:32.658 --> 36:34.493
Thank you.

36:34.526 --> 36:36.428
What?
The baker says
it's a boy!

36:36.462 --> 36:37.896
It's a boy?
It's a boy.

36:37.929 --> 36:40.299
It's a boy?!
(laughing)

36:41.533 --> 36:43.635
You're right.

36:43.669 --> 36:46.338
It should have been my baby.

36:46.372 --> 36:50.276
To be fair: Luisa didn't know
 Petra had Rafael's sperm.

36:50.309 --> 36:52.644
There's still a chance
with you and Raf.

36:52.678 --> 36:54.946
I swear.

36:54.980 --> 36:56.948
And so it was

36:56.982 --> 36:58.984
that after
 a quick Google search,

36:59.017 --> 37:02.488
and some pointers
 from fertilitygoddess1345...

37:02.521 --> 37:04.690
(doorbell rings)

37:06.458 --> 37:09.261
A sandwich and the
extra turkey baster?

37:09.295 --> 37:10.696
Perfect. Thank you.

37:12.298 --> 37:14.700
...Petra decideth...

37:14.733 --> 37:17.636
to go for it.

37:17.669 --> 37:20.238
*

37:28.747 --> 37:30.716
DOCTOR:
Okay, it looks like
Mateo is...

37:30.749 --> 37:32.551
seven pounds
and two ounces.

37:32.584 --> 37:33.985
What?!

37:34.019 --> 37:35.821
That's better
than before.
(laughing)

37:35.854 --> 37:37.456
We hug now, right?

37:37.489 --> 37:39.558
Yes.
(sighs)

37:39.591 --> 37:41.427
And I'm impressed.
Good job.

37:41.460 --> 37:42.861
(happy squeal)
Go-go tell your mom.

37:42.894 --> 37:44.530
Okay.

37:44.563 --> 37:46.565
Better than before?

37:46.598 --> 37:48.434
Yes! Okay,
I'm going back in.

37:50.035 --> 37:52.838
(laughs)
(panting)

37:52.871 --> 37:55.474
(sighs, panting)

37:58.777 --> 38:00.646
Yeah, I think
I'm just overwhelmed.

38:00.679 --> 38:02.914
Mm.
(sighs)

38:09.955 --> 38:12.658
I've just been
so worried about her.

38:19.565 --> 38:22.668
So... I think there's something

38:22.701 --> 38:24.703
I should tell you and Jane...

38:24.736 --> 38:27.973
now that everything's okay.

38:28.006 --> 38:30.742
By the power vested in me
by the state of Nevada

38:30.776 --> 38:33.845
and the goddess Cher,
who is with us here in spirit,

38:33.879 --> 38:35.947
I now pronounce you man
and wife.

38:35.981 --> 38:37.649
(applause and cheering)

38:37.683 --> 38:40.752
You got married?
By a Cher impersonator?

38:40.786 --> 38:43.622
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
 * Oh, if they could
 turn back time. *

38:43.655 --> 38:45.357
It was obviously
a mistake.

38:45.391 --> 38:47.793
We're getting
it annulled.

38:51.730 --> 38:53.399
Abuela!
Ma!

38:53.432 --> 38:55.967
(laughing)
 ¿Qué?

38:56.001 --> 38:58.470
(laughter)

38:59.738 --> 39:01.006
Morning, boss.

39:01.039 --> 39:02.674
It's not a good time, Scott.

39:02.708 --> 39:04.510
Oh, I'll be quick.

39:04.543 --> 39:06.378
I just wanted to
discuss the fact

39:06.412 --> 39:08.480
that you stole
Mr. Solano's sperm?

39:08.514 --> 39:10.048
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
 Oh, Petra.

39:10.081 --> 39:13.118
You thought
 you got off scot-free.

39:29.801 --> 39:32.003
(smacks his lips)

39:33.171 --> 39:35.774
Home, huh?

39:35.807 --> 39:37.509
Just wanted to make sure

39:37.543 --> 39:39.978
there were no more
crazy people around.

39:40.011 --> 39:42.548
Mm-hmm.

39:42.581 --> 39:46.985
You know, I haven't had a
chance to say thank you.

39:48.720 --> 39:51.823
For... I don't know.

39:51.857 --> 39:53.792
How do you say...
 for everything?

39:53.825 --> 39:55.527
For everything.

39:55.561 --> 39:57.463
Oh, of course.

39:57.496 --> 39:58.997
You know... anything.

39:59.030 --> 40:00.866
All in a day's work

40:00.899 --> 40:02.834
for our Villanueva
 family advisor.

40:02.868 --> 40:05.136
So, you know Rafael's
staying over.
Oh, I know.

40:05.170 --> 40:07.539
No, but, like, just
as the baby's father.

40:07.573 --> 40:09.808
Huh? You don't tell that
 to an advisor.

40:09.841 --> 40:13.044
That was weird. I don't even
know why I'm telling you that.

40:13.078 --> 40:15.614
But Michael knew exactly why.

40:22.854 --> 40:25.023
No.

40:25.056 --> 40:28.760
I just wanted to try some
skin-to-skin contact.

40:28.794 --> 40:29.995
What?

40:30.028 --> 40:32.531
Well, it helps babies bond
with their dads.

40:32.564 --> 40:33.999
It's, uh, chapter
12 in the book.

40:34.032 --> 40:35.734
Oh, right. Yeah.
Yeah, I read that.

40:35.767 --> 40:37.135
It was a really cool chapter.

40:37.168 --> 40:40.806
So I should probably
go to sleep.

40:40.839 --> 40:43.141
I have to be up in, um...

40:43.174 --> 40:45.243
121 minutes.

40:45.276 --> 40:46.812
(laughs)
Okay.

40:46.845 --> 40:48.246
Good night.

40:48.279 --> 40:50.882
Night.

40:55.521 --> 40:57.723
(baby coos softly)

41:04.796 --> 41:07.599
This is a little weird.

41:07.633 --> 41:10.602
Yeah, but it was always
gonna be weird.

41:10.636 --> 41:12.037
True.

41:12.070 --> 41:14.105
And it's actually kind of...

41:14.139 --> 41:16.207
regular weird.

41:16.241 --> 41:18.009
Which is good?

41:18.043 --> 41:20.912
Yeah. It's really good.

41:22.748 --> 41:25.083
And so it was.

41:25.116 --> 41:27.553
For now.

41:29.755 --> 41:32.490
Oh, wait, I forgot one thing.

41:33.559 --> 41:35.727
(beeps)

41:43.001 --> 41:45.904
(speaking German)

41:47.773 --> 41:49.608
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
 I could really use some

41:49.641 --> 41:52.878
"it's-going-to-be-okay"
 theme music right about now.

